frames.caption: A lone figure stands on a rocky ledge overlooking a sprawling cityscape, drenched in rain. The city below is illuminated with glowing lights, creating a stark contrast against the dark, stormy atmosphere. The person appears contemplative, gazing into the distance as rain pours down.
frames.description: The scene depicts a solitary individual standing atop a high, rocky outcrop, looking out over a vast, illuminated city during a rainstorm. The setting suggests a moment of introspection or decision-making, with the dramatic weather adding to the emotional weight of the scene.

frames.caption: A person stands on a rocky outcrop overlooking a sprawling cityscape at dusk. The city lights begin to illuminate the skyline as the sun sets, casting a serene glow over the scene.
frames.description: The scene captures a solitary figure standing atop a rocky peak, gazing out over a vast city. The setting is urban, with skyscrapers and city lights creating a vibrant backdrop against the dimming sky.
